data.description: Discover a charming 2-bed, 2-story townhouse in coveted South Side Flats, offering an exciting urban lifestyle. Natural light fills the living/dining room, while the well-equipped kitchen features granite counters and ample storage. Step outside to the serene rear patio with a privacy fence. Upstairs, two bedrooms boast double closets, and the updated ceramic tile bath showcases a granite counter and contemporary sink. This home grants access to a wealth of amenities within walking distance, including trendy restaurants, cozy cafes, boutique shops, and vibrant nightlife. With convenient access to public transportation and major roads, citywide commuting is a breeze. Immerse yourself in the arts and culture scenes just moments away. Outdoor enthusiasts will relish the nearby parks, perfect for hiking, biking, and connecting with nature.
